### 7.3 H3 Decision Device

Three-layer architecture with confidence-weighted voting:
- Layer 1: input → 64 (threshold 0.3)
- Layer 2: 64 → 32 (threshold 0.5)
- Layer 3: 32 → actions (threshold 0.7)

